{"tid":1254974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東茂名市政協主席黃心強溺死","createTime":"2019-06-24T10:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T10:45:33.000Z","uid":263484,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d99890f353b37ff5507a8b68fc621f3c67da9885","tid":1254974,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"咩事咁睇唔開?<br />\n茂名係咪好多死豬???<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190624/large/1561365714_8d21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190624%2Flarge%2F1561365714_8d21.jpg&h=af4e1f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【死因待確定】廣東茂名市政協主席黃心強溺死 官方：是否自殺仍未定性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東茂名市政協主席黃心強上周五（21日）早上7時半，被發現溺水死亡。官方消息指，黃心強是否自殺，仍有待調查。<br />\n黃心強的遺體於上周五在湛江市赤坎區附近海邊被發現，屍體表面並無傷痕，基本符合溺水死亡特徵。市政府相關負責人表示，警方正進一步調查，下一步會安排屍檢，是否自殺，目前還未有結論。<br />\n茂名市政協相關負責人亦稱，黃心強是否自殺，目前仍未定性。他又指，事發前，黃心強在工作上並無異樣。<br />\n官方簡歷顯示，黃心強是廣東雷州人，生於1959年1月，1976年10月入黨，長年在廣東茂名工作，曾任副市長、市委常委、<strong>市統戰部部長</strong>、市人民政府黨組副書記等職務。2016年6月起，擔任茂名市政協主席、黨組書記。他最後一次露面，是本月18日參加茂名市政協辦公室舉行的「扶貧濟困日」捐款活動。<br />\n2010年5月，因為拖建「天下第一爛」省道（茂名省道281線七那段），包括時任茂名市副市長黃心強在內的8名茂名官員受到相應處分。<br />\n上游新聞／《廣州日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190624/59752033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190624%2F59752033&d=YuwHWJ3tJNmBkarA42FFVEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=89018653\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190624%2F59752033&h=cc4323a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190624/59752033</a>"},{"pid":"735c4bf33fe66f75e98389fca77879000f2a65d9","tid":1254974,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"預言：抑鬱自殺"},{"pid":"63326ea31c6373e5208c8d80ca425bf73e45adde","tid":1254974,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:27:53.000Z","msg":"有新意"},{"pid":"7e267f5aa9f9c38f8ce14ffb64a884fac0ab1efe","tid":1254974,"uid":119667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:31:01.000Z","msg":"抑鬱"},{"pid":"322456e4f455bab0759bc55e8e09126710d2a2ca","tid":1254974,"uid":81113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"735c4bf33fe66f75e98389fca77879000f2a65d9","tid":1254974,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:26:29.000Z","msg":"預言：抑鬱自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:32:39.000Z","msg":"其實寫曬出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>廣東茂名市政協主席黃心強上周五（21日）早上7時半，<span style=\"color: red;\">被</span>發現<span style=\"color: red;\">溺</span>水<span style=\"color: red;\">死</span>亡。官方消息指，黃心強是否自殺，仍有待調查。<br />\n黃心強的遺體於上周五在湛江市赤坎區附近海邊被發現，屍體表面並無傷痕，基本符合溺水死亡特徵。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d50f00c5744e3baaf9cd03dc94d8ba5d2cd20f1","tid":1254974,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:33:44.000Z","msg":"跣腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fffe9e5cc70068b57ad54ce964f43b7d89408a6","tid":1254974,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:33:46.000Z","msg":"直接掉落海"},{"pid":"a65a2a918c4fe4e03f4392e7d58f7ace85722c9c","tid":1254974,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"勁並勁共勁共～"},{"pid":"40804ecf6458c1bf0032a8cb709b281952d500e7","tid":1254974,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"一時間搵唔倒佢d黑材料/d黑材料唔夠爆 又好想佢死 咪製造意外囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a66abb108a6cd825cc4902bfaaab9b1d2a60ce48","tid":1254974,"uid":263484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>本月18日參加茂名市政協辦公室舉行的「扶貧濟困日」捐款活動。</stron